<item>
            <title>[LU-17767] error: &apos;struct lsmcontext&apos; has no member named &apos;slot&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17767</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Building Lustre with kernel 6.8.0-31-generic failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;  CC [M]  /root/lustre-release/libcfs/libcfs/linux/linux-prim.o
In file included from /root/lustre-release/libcfs/libcfs/linux/linux-prim.c:49:
/root/lustre-release/lustre/include/lustre_compat.h: In function &apos;lsmcontext_init&apos;:
/root/lustre-release/lustre/include/lustre_compat.h:760:11: error: &apos;struct lsmcontext&apos; has no member named &apos;slot&apos;
  760 |         cp-&amp;gt;slot = slot;
      |           ^~
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://git.launchpad.net/~ubuntu-kernel/ubuntu/+source/linux/+git/noble/commit/include/linux/security.h?h=Ubuntu-6.8.0-22.22&amp;amp;id=dad7cffb719e45fd43121ade4ada90ff376c9cad&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git.launchpad.net/~ubuntu-kernel/ubuntu/+source/linux/+git/noble/commit/include/linux/security.h?h=Ubuntu-6.8.0-22.22&amp;amp;id=dad7cffb719e45fd43121ade4ada90ff376c9cad&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
